  m_text: 'The escape has begun!

    Press and hold the screen to inflate the balloon
    and fly UP. Release to deflate and dive DOWN.

    Swipe left and right to maneuver
    around deadly traps.

    Remember: the bigger the balloon, the easier it is
    to pop, so shrink in time to slip through narrow passages.

    Rise as high
    as possible and collect coins to unlock new skins!'
